articles.title: Dragon Ball Super: Super Hero Gives Super Saiyan 4 a Unique Twist
articles.author: Comic Book
articles.summary: Dragon Ball Super: Super Hero introduces a new version of Super Saiyan 4 Goku. Neva's Namekian magic sparks the transformation, changing Goku's clothes and giving him red hair, resembling Super Saiyan God. This new version of the transformation also magically changes Goku's clothes in the process too just like the old non-canonical version.

articles.title: These 34 Problem-Solving Products Are Downright Perfect
articles.author: Taylor Steele
articles.summary: The Pink Stuff cleaning paste is introduced as a solution for removing stains and dirt. Handy Laundry launches extra-large wool dryer balls, an alternative to toxic dryer sheets. O'Keeffe's night lip treatment is presented as a reparative solution with beeswax and shea butter for refreshed lips.

articles.title: WATCH: Hogs stumble in College Station
articles.author: Jacob Morris
articles.summary: Dyson Gen5outsize Absolute features strong suction power, sleek design, and cutting-edge technology. It is a product from Dyson.

articles.title: Lidl fans set to love €24.99 ‘splash-free' gadget that will banish moss & dirt from patio – it hits middle aisle in days
articles.author: Isabela Boechat
articles.summary: LIDL Ireland has launched a Surface Cleaner for €24.99, designed for cleaning outdoor surfaces like patios and garage doors, which will be available starting February 20. Additionally, Lidl released a cordless vacuum cleaner priced at €59.99, available starting February 10. The vacuum can be used as a handheld or upright cleaner, offering two suction modes.

articles.title: PHȲND: $10 Million (Seed) Raised For Advancing Smart TV Gaming Platform
articles.author: Amit Chowdhry
articles.summary: PHȲND, a subscription-free cloud gaming platform, is set to launch a beta version in 2025 after securing $10 million in seed funding. The platform aims to make high-quality gaming accessible on smart TVs and connected devices, offering a free-to-play experience while providing new advertising opportunities for brands within the gaming audience.

articles.title: This TikTok-Viral Beauty Brand Just Launched A Setting Powder That Gives Filter-Like Results
articles.summary: Wonderskin, a beauty brand, is promoting its new product, the Wonderskin FYP Powder. The powder aims to minimize pores and absorb excess shine, potentially offering more benefits than setting sprays.

articles.title: WATCH: Class of 2026 Official Visits
articles.author: Jacob Morris
articles.summary: Dyson's Gen5outsize Absolute vacuum cleaner features strong suction power, a sleek design, and cutting-edge technology, suggesting an introduction or promotion of a new product.

articles.title: Namaa EXP unveils M STREET Heliopolis with EGP 4bn investment
articles.author: Daily News Egypt
articles.summary: Namaa EXP has launched its new brand, M STREET. M STREET introduces a premium shopping and entertainment experience. M STREET brings together top local and international brands under the concept of shopping indulgence.

articles.title: This TikTok-Viral Beauty Brand Just Launched The Setting Powder To End All Setting Powders
articles.author: Marissa De Santis
articles.summary: Wonderskin has launched its new product, FYP Filter Powder, a pressed powder designed to mattify skin and set makeup for extended wear. The powder utilizes light-diffusing technology to create a soft-focus effect, blurring pores and imperfections. The product is currently offered in a bundle and is translucent, suitable for all skin tones.

articles.title: Makeover: Drug store dupes for those coveted luxury brand lipsticks
articles.author: Nadia Albano
articles.summary: Revlon is introducing its Super Lustrous Lipsticks line as affordable alternatives to luxury brands like Charlotte Tillbury, MAC Cosmetics, and Nars. The lipsticks come in various shades like Primrose (dupe for Charlotte Tillbury's Pillow Talk Fair), Pink Promise (similar to MAC's Candy Yum Yum), Rumberry (similar to Nars' Bewitched), and Really Red (alternative to MAC's Ruby Woo), offering diverse color options and finishes.

articles.title: Nokia 3310 Gets a Modern USB-C Upgrade
articles.author: archyde
articles.summary: Andrea has created and launched a USB-C adapter for the classic Nokia 3310 phone. This adapter seamlessly replaces the original charging port, integrating a USB-C connector while retaining the phone's original hardware. The aim is to bridge the gap between nostalgia and modern use, allowing users to connect the phone to modern accessories.

articles.title: Live From New York: How SNL's 50-Year Legacy Turned Comedy Into Culture—and Commerce
articles.author: Kate Hardcastle
articles.summary: Saks Fifth Avenue launched an exclusive collection featuring SNL-inspired sweatshirts and accessories. Le Labo released a limited-edition candle with SNL-themed packaging, and Favorite Daughter introduced a line of t-shirts and baseball caps. These collaborations celebrate SNL's 50th anniversary and demonstrate the show's enduring influence on consumer products.

articles.title: Coming to a town near you: a tech-savvy ice cream truck
articles.author: Timothy Malcolm
articles.summary: Alsies, a technology-driven ice cream truck brand, is expanding to the Dallas-Fort Worth metroplex in Texas, bringing its app-based tracking and on-demand service to the region. With franchised trucks equipped with geo-fencing and a diverse menu of frozen treats, Alsies aims to reimagine the traditional ice cream truck experience.

articles.title: ADB Makes Me Feel Like an Android Hacker, But It's Super Useful
articles.author: Patrick Campanale
articles.summary: Epic Games released its own games store for mobile. Users can install the Epic Games Store APK on their Android phones using ADB (Android Debug Bridge) to access titles like Fortnite outside official channels. This allows Epic to distribute directly to the end user bypassing Apple and Google.

articles.title: Ace age
articles.author: Kap Maceda
articles.summary: Mini Philippines launched the all-electric Mini Aceman, a crossover model priced at P3.55 million, featuring a 54.2-kWh battery offering up to 407 kilometers of range. Additionally, they unveiled the newest iteration of the Mini Cooper Five-Door, priced at P3.799 million, powered by a 2.0-liter Mini TwinPower Turbo engine.

articles.title: Nubia Blade A35E, the starting model, hot model! Sales through 10,000 units in less than a month
articles.author: archyde
articles.summary: Nubia recently launched the Nubia Blade A35E smartphone in Thailand, targeting first-time smartphone users. It features a 6.52-inch display, Octa-Core processor, 6GB of RAM, 64GB internal storage, a 5,000 mAh battery, and an 8MP rear camera, priced at 1,999 Baht. Nubia is exploring expanding the availability of the Blade A35E to other markets.

articles.title: Spinneys Expands and Reaches the Coastal Resort Town of Ain Sukhna
articles.summary: Spinneys has launched its 31st store in Ain Sukhna, Egypt, featuring over 20,000 SKUs, including 2,500 private label products. Customers can also place orders through the delivery platform by ordering online at www.spinneys-egypt.com or via the Spinneys hotline 16005 and the Spinneys mobile application.

articles.title: Samsung Galaxy S25: Price Plunges After Release – Cdiscount Offer!
articles.author: archyde
articles.summary: Samsung has launched the Galaxy S25, a smartphone featuring Galaxy AI, an advanced camera system with a 12MP ultra-wide angle sensor, a 10MP telephoto lens with X3 optical Zoom, and a 50MP main camera. Currently, Cdiscount offers the phone at a discounted price, providing an opportune time to upgrade.

articles.title: 'Life-changing' product gets rid of dust better than regular vacuum for fraction of price
articles.author: Jess Flaherty
articles.summary: Kärcher's KWD 1 model, designed for versatile cleaning, has received positive feedback as a powerful alternative to traditional vacuum cleaners. Users on Reddit are praising its ability to handle both wet and dry messes, with comparisons made to Dyson and Henry vacuums.

articles.title: Vax carpet cleaner for pet owners has been reduced by 42% on Amazon
articles.author: Nisha Mal
articles.summary: Amazon is offering a significant discount on the Vax Dual Power Pet Advance Carpet Cleaner, reducing the price from £169.99 to £99. Customers have praised the product's cleaning capabilities, ease of use, and compact design for pet owners. Other products by Vax like Vax Platinum Smart Wash Carpet Cleaner and Vax Rapid Power Pro Upright Carpet Cleaner also mentioned in the content.

articles.title: These Are the Benefits of Letting Windows Invade Your Privacy
articles.author: Yadullah Abidi
articles.summary: Microsoft launched Windows Recall, a controversial feature that periodically takes screenshots of PC activity and uses CoPilot to enable content search.  Microsoft claims to have fixed security vulnerabilities and addresses the privacy concerns. Data collection from users helps Microsoft improve Windows and its features.

articles.title: Amazon 'nippy little lawn mower' reduced to £60 and 'couldn't be easier to use'
articles.author: Emily Chaplin
articles.summary: Amazon shoppers have discovered the Flymo Easi Glide 300 hover mower, designed for small to medium-sized lawns, noted for its lightweight design, ambidextrous handles, and ease of use. The mower features a 10m cable and folds flat for storage; it is available for purchase on Amazon, and Argos has reduced its price.

articles.title: An update on the new Windows 11
articles.author: Rich Warren
articles.summary: Microsoft's Windows 11 can run on older PCs, but the company doesn't guarantee updates, potentially affecting security. Netflix has increased the cost of its standard, ad-free streaming account by $2.50 a month. Apple has also increased its streaming fee by a similar amount.

articles.title: Attention Publix enthusiasts! Rejoice as a softer sandwich roll has arrived.
articles.author: Internewscast
articles.summary: Publix has launched a new soft white sub roll, baked fresh in-store, and available year-round. The new bread offering is available to Publix customers starting Saturday and joins the existing lineup of sub rolls and wraps.

articles.title: Li Hongyi's GovTech department demos 45 products that "serve the public good" Singapore News
articles.summary: Open Government Products (OGP) division, under Li Hongyi, showcased 45 products designed for public use at their Demo Day. During its hackathon, the team developed prototypes like Bridge, a scheduling tool for medical transport, Hawkernomics, an educational game, and Spaceship, an AI-powered tool for creating tech prototypes. The company aims to bring these projects live in the coming year.

articles.title: The New Tesla Model Y Is Imminent: Keep Your Eye On The Price
articles.author: Forbes
articles.summary: A new 'Juniper' Model Y is nearing release. Lower-priced variants of the car are expected to follow soon.

articles.title: The New Tesla Model Y Is Imminent: Keep Your Eye On The Price
articles.summary: Tesla is launching a new Model Y, initially available as a high-priced Launch edition priced at $52,490 with the federal tax credit, which is expected to be available in March. Base Dual-Motor and Rear-Wheel Drive versions will be released later in the year at a considerably lower price point.

articles.title: Sandton entrepreneur launches a groundbreaking tech platform
articles.author: Print Content
articles.summary: Priven Reddy launched Codeblaze.ai, a new AI platform designed to revolutionize software development. The platform allows users to build full-stack applications using natural language commands, eliminating the need for complex coding skills. Codeblaze.ai handles the entire software creation process, from code generation to deployment and scaling, and had its early access debut in Dubai.

articles.title: 10 Handy Tasty Kitchen Items That Are Eternally Useful, So You'll Never Regret Buying ‘Em
articles.author: Brock Pirtle
articles.summary: Walmart has launched a variety of new kitchen and cooking products under the 'Tasty' collection. The collection includes a 24-piece nonstick cookware set, a glass popcorn popper, donut pans, a carbon steel wok, a charcuterie tray, a jumbo sauté pan, a cutting board prep station, steak knives, grippy tongs, and a stainless-steel knife set.

articles.title: Elon Musk's 'smartest AI on earth' ready for take-off
articles.summary: Elon Musk is preparing to launch xAI's Grok 3, an AI chatbot designed to compete with ChatGPT. The unveiling, including a live demo, is scheduled for Tuesday at 3pm Sydney time. Musk stated Grok 3 is in the final stages of development and exhibits powerful reasoning capabilities, outperforming existing chatbots in tests.

articles.title: Sky launches brand new 4K TV deal
articles.author: Christopher Harper
articles.summary: Sky has launched the second generation of Sky Glass TV, featuring enhanced 4K HDR image quality, Quantum Dot technology, and a built-in Dolby Atmos sound system. Sky Glass Gen 2 eliminates the need for a satellite dish by streaming over Wi-Fi. The company also announced new affordable pricing, with Sky's Essential TV pack starting at £15 per month.

articles.title: Sky launches brand new 4K TV deal - it's more affordable than ever
articles.author: Christopher Harper
articles.summary: Sky has launched the second generation of Sky Glass TV, featuring enhanced 4K HDR image quality, Dolby Atmos sound, and integrated Sky TV. The new Sky Glass offers new Essential TV pack from £15 a month and is available through interest-free monthly payments from £14 per month with flexible subscription options.

articles.title: Sky launches brand new 4K TV deal - it's more affordable than ever
articles.author: Christopher Harper
articles.summary: Sky has launched Sky Glass Gen 2, its latest television offering, featuring enhanced picture and sound, interactive voice commands, and affordability options.  New customers can access Sky's Essential TV pack for £15 a month, or purchase Sky Glass through interest-free monthly payments starting at £14.

articles.title: Chinese sex doll maker sees jump in 2025 sales as AI boosts adult toys' user experience
articles.author: South China Morning Post
articles.summary: WMDoll is launching its new MetaBox series of sex dolls powered by large language models (LLMs). The new dolls offer improved responsiveness, interactivity, and multiple personalities and are priced US$100-200 higher than existing models, with additional monthly token usage charges after the first year. WMDoll is also working on wearable devices to give non-AI toys access to LLMs and lifelike facial expressions for the dolls.

articles.title: £40 Dunelm scrubber customers 'can't keep house clean without'
articles.author: Husna Anjum
articles.summary: Dunelm is promoting its Hurricane Spin Scrubber, a cordless and rechargeable device effective for cleaning soap scum, water stains, wheels, and garden furniture. The product boasts a powerful 25W motor for efficient cleaning, and customer reviews highlight its ease of use and effectiveness. Debenhams also offers a scrubber for cleaning purposes.

articles.title: Uptake of technology, scale of population, and local innovation make India an exciting market: Cameron Adams
articles.author: ETtech
articles.summary: Canva is investing in tailoring its platform for the Indian market. This includes launching a Hindi website to provide a localized user experience and offering one- and seven-day subscriptions specific to Indian users. The integration of AI is also empowering users to create designs and explore creative ideas.

articles.title: The Brand Auditors Expands Services with Transformation AI Marketing Consulting
articles.author: Newsfile
articles.summary: The Brand Auditors is offering innovative AI services to help clients future-proof their marketing strategies. This new service aims to drive revenue growth, enhance customer engagement, and reduce marketing waste.

articles.title: The Brand Auditors Expands Services with Transformation AI Marketing Consulting
articles.author: Newsfile
articles.summary: The Brand Auditors introduces innovative AI as a service to help clients future-proof marketing strategies. This AI-driven service aims to drive revenue growth, enhance customer engagement, and reduce marketing waste.

articles.title: Mini EV from Vietnam is sold in Indonesia for 200 million
articles.author: archyde
articles.summary: Vinfast launched the VF3 Mini EV in Indonesia, priced at Rp227 million, targeting urban dwellers. The electric vehicle features a 40 HP motor, a range of 215 kilometers, and compact dimensions suitable for city driving. The VF3 boasts rapid charging, enabling a charge from 10% to 70% in just 36 minutes.

articles.title: Dragons' Den's Noelle O'Connor can sell sunless tan to the Californians – but she's no fake
articles.author: Fearghal O'Connor
articles.summary: The Kind Brand Company, founded by Noelle O'Connor, is expanding its TanOrganic range of tanning and skincare products into the US market. The company specializes in 'sunless' tan products.

articles.title: 7 Shower Gels You Need for Bright, Glowing Skin
articles.summary: Olay launched the Cleansing and Nourishing Body Wash with Hyaluronic Acid, featuring hyaluronic acid, shea butter, and niacinamide. Nécessaire introduced The Body Wash (Vitamin C) with vitamin C, niacinamide, vitamins C and E, and three different enzymes. Dove released the Glowing Ritual Body Wash with Lotus Flower and Rice Water, harnessing lotus flowers and rice water. Tree Hut launched Vitamin C Shea Sugar Body Wash with vitamin C and shea butter. Sol de Janeiro introduced Brazilian 4 Play Moisturizing Shower Cream-Gel with cupuaçu butter, coconut oil, and acai. Bioderma launched Atoderm Hydrating Shower Gel and The Glow Getter Multi-Oil Hydrating Body Wash.

articles.title: Holy Grail Skincare Products And Hair Hacks That Deliver Visible Results
articles.author: Buzz Feed
articles.summary: Several skincare and hair care products are highlighted for their effectiveness based on user reviews. The products include eye creams that reduce dark circles and puffiness, snail mucin hand cream for hydration, kojic acid soap for even skin tone, and a dry shampoo to revive greasy hair. Additionally, a callus removal gel and an eight-second hair treatment are mentioned for improving skin and hair health, respectively.

articles.title: Argos shoppers race to buy �22 Revolution beauty gift set reduced to just �5.53
articles.author: Manchester Evening News
articles.summary: Argos is offering Revolution skincare essentials at a promotional price of 69p each.

articles.title: Lexus Unveils the All-New LX 700h and Enhanced LX Series with Advanced Hybrid Innovations
articles.author: Eye
articles.summary: Lexus introduces the LX 700h, a new electrified addition to the LX series, marking a significant step towards the company's commitment to carbon neutrality. This enhancement aims to deliver effortless and refined driving experiences for customers.

articles.title: Makeover: Drug store dupes for those coveted luxury brand lipsticks
articles.author: Canoe
articles.summary: Revlon Super Lustrous Lipsticks are being compared to luxury brand lipsticks. The comparison aims to find drugstore dupes and offer a similar look for a lower price.

articles.title: Cool, calm and connected: Updated 2025 Nissan QASHQAI introduces new N-DESIGN grade and debuts Nissan Connected Car Services (Nissan Motor Co (Australia) Pty Ltd)
articles.author: Public Technologies
articles.summary: Nissan is launching the 2025 Nissan QASHQAI with a revised exterior design, elevated interior, and a new N-DESIGN grade. The updated vehicle will feature Nissan Connected Car Services and remain available with e-POWER.

articles.title: I tested the Lexar NM790 with Heatsink for a month, and it's easily the best ...
articles.author: Tech Radar
articles.summary: Lexar is offering the NM790 at a competitive price, especially in higher capacities. The NM790 provides reasonable performance for its price point.

articles.title: Entrepreneur bridges digital divide with tech solutions and skills training
articles.author: Independent online
articles.summary: Sayda Communication, founded by Tsholofelo Nowalaza, is launching a full-service digital solutions company. This company provides services like website building, social media ads, marketing strategies, IT training, and robotics and coding for young learners. These services aim to empower people and help businesses grow through digital skills.
